@NODE Introduction
@TITLE "wave.player · Introduction"


    @{b}Introduction@{ub}


    wave.player is a player plugin for AmiNetRadio (@{" website " system "OpenURL http://anr.amigazeux.net/" })
    which adds support for RIFF WAVE and RIFF WAVE Extensible sample files,
    usually files which end with a ".wav" suffix.


    Following subformats are supported currently:

    * 8bit PCM mono/ stereo

    * 16bit PCM mono/ stereo

    * 24bit PCM mono/ stereo

    * 32bit PCM mono/ stereo


    * 12bit PCM mono/ stereo

    (other intermediate bit sizes should work too, but are untested.)


    * A-law 

    * µ-law 

    * 32bit IEEE Float

    * 64bit IEEE Float 

@ENDNODE

@NODE Requirements
@TITLE "wave.player · Requirements"


